<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raphael Sanzio-coins analysis</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/cropper.css">


</head>


<body>

    <div class="heading">
        <div class="heading-content">
            <h1>Raphael Sanzio paintings-coins matching</h1>
            <p>(Η εφαρμογή παρουσιάζει έναν αυτοματοποιημένο τρόπο εύρεσης μοτίβων ανάμεσα στους πίνακες του Raphael και σε αρχαιοελληνικά/ρωμαϊκά νομίσματα)</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-containers">
        <div class="grid-container">
            <!-- First column: Small Images Container -->
            <div class="small-images-container">
                <h2>1. Select a painting</h2>
                <div class="image-grid">
                    <!-- Small images will be displayed here -->
                </div>
                
            </div>
    
            <!-- Second column: Expanded Image Container and Coins Container -->
            <div class="expanded-images-container" >
                <!-- Expanded Image Container -->
                <div class="step2-heading" style="display: none;">
                    <h2>2. Crop the part of the image you want to search</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="expanded-image-container">
                    <div id="cropperContainer">
                        <img class="expanded-image" src="" alt="Expanded Image">
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn1">Search for coins</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="coins-container" style="display:none;">
    
    </div>
    <div class="restartbtn">
        <button class="toggle-button" style="display:none"></button>
    </div>
    

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <!-- Decorative Elements -->
                <div class="footer-decorations">
                    <div class="decoration-circle"></div>
                    <div class="decoration-line"></div>
                    <div class="decoration-circle"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Legal Information -->
                <div class="legal-info">
                    <p>&copy; 2023 Raphael Sanzio Paintings</p>
                    <p>Privacy Policy</p>
                    <p>Terms of Service</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Decorative Elements -->
                <div class="footer-decorations">
                    <div class="decoration-circle"></div>
                    <div class="decoration-line"></div>
                    <div class="decoration-circle"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <div class="loading-spinner">
        <div class="spinner"></div>
        <div class="loading-text">Searching for Coins...</div>
    </div>








</body>
<script src="/javascripts/main.js" defer></script>
<script src="/cropper.js"></script>

</html>